    ArgoWF -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>SA Token"| K8sAPI
    PersistAgent -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>SA Token"| K8sAPI
    DSPOCtrl -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>SA Token"| K8sAPI
